&lt;center&gt;![Why should you pick NodeServ?](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/sections/why.png)&lt;/center&gt;

&lt;center&gt;![Fast Support](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/sections/fast-support.png)&lt;/center&gt;
NodeServ is run by a duo that takes support very seriously, we will always try to get back to you as soon as possible! In fact, we have made it easier for our customers to contact us by offering:

&lt;center&gt;![Phone (+1 (321)-214-0912), IRC (#NodeServ on irc.freenode.net), and Email (support@nodeserv.com)](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/sections/contact.png "Phone/IRC/Email")&lt;/center&gt;

&lt;center&gt;![Our Average Ticket Response Time](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/sections/tickets.png)&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;![Response Time](https://nodeserv.com/let/support-time/time.php)&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;(Updates in realtime)&lt;/center&gt;

&lt;br /&gt;

&lt;center&gt;![5 Day Money Back Guarantee(*)](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/sections/guarantee.png)&lt;/center&gt;
At NodeServ we believe everyone should have a chance to try our service, as well as chance to test out our customer support or even hang out with us in [IRC](https://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=NodeServ). That is why we offer a no questions asked 5 day money back guarantee on our services. Feel free to check out our [Refund Agreement](https://nodeserv.com/legal/refunds) for more information!

&lt;br /&gt;

&lt;center&gt;![Reasonable SLA](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/sections/sla.png)&lt;/center&gt;
We are one of the few companies that do not try to unrealistically promise our clients the world. That's why NodeServ can comfortably offer a 99.99% Uptime on our services. However if we do have a problem we try to maintain communication with our customers through our [billing area](https://billing.nodeserv.com) as well as our [IRC channel](https://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=NodeServ) to provide up to the minute information on our resolution. In the unlikely event that we do have downtime, you can request account credits according to our [SLA Agreement](https://nodeserv.com/legal/sla).

&lt;br /&gt;

&lt;center&gt;![Low Abuse](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/sections/abuse.png)&lt;/center&gt;
Our services are heavily monitored to prevent trolls, spammers, and abusers from disrupting our other customers. If you want a server that runs fast and smooth, NodeServ should definitely be on your list. You can check out our [AUP](https://nodeserv.com/legal/aup) and [TOS](https://nodeserv.com/legal/tos) for more information on what you can and can't do on our services (better to read now than be sorry later)

&lt;center&gt;![Page Separator](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/separator.png)&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;![Aspiring Entrepreneurs](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/sections/aspiring-entrepreneur.png)&lt;/center&gt;

Want to become a reseller and resell our VPS's? If so NodeServ offers an awesome "À la carte" reseller program.
We give you the ability to mix and match resources to create x amount of containers to resell to your clients.

&lt;center&gt;![VPS Reseller Prices](https://nodeserv.com/let/plans/vps-reseller.png)&lt;/center&gt;

If you are interested please submit a ticket with our sales department, and we'll get back to you shortly. We can do custom quotes to anyone who needs a specific monthly amount of resources.

&lt;br /&gt;

&lt;center&gt;![Begin Footer](https://nodeserv.com/let/common/separator.png)&lt;/center&gt;

*Money back guarantee only applies if the AUP or TOS have not been breached / Only applicable to first purchase.

